  ∧
  riemannZeta.N' σ T ≤ KLN.CC₁ I.H₀ α d δ k H σ * (log (k * T))^(2*σ) * (log T)^(5 - 4*σ) * T^(8/3*(1-σ)) / (2 * π * d) + KLN.CC₂ I.H₀ d η k H μ σ * (log T)^2 / (2 * π * d) := by 
